long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Go To Dot is a fun arcade game where we try to get the ball to the goal by paying attention to the obstacles we encounter.

We are trying to get a ball to the point in the game. In the meantime, we move forward by paying attention to the difficult obstacles and getting points by getting the ball to the end. With the points we have achieved, we can be partners in this adventure for a long time by maintaining our high score goal. Reach the Point has emerged as a skill game prepared for us, those who love children's games, as it is fun and challenging.

To swipe Install this extension to play the  Go To Dot game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads.
